{
  "texts": [
    "We manage these complex elements within the modules using templates, which ensures a well-organized structure.",
    "Furthermore, we have developed numerous base templates and created new templates by inheriting from these base templates.",
    "These templates are reusable by the models, enhancing their reusability.",
    "It should be noted that since all models share the same configuration reading method and log storage path management, these two modules are called in a common, model-independent area.",
    "In this case, there is no need for the template-based design for them."
  ]
}